  <p class="text-muted txt-left bd-left-red fs-7">Learn about GraphQL, how it works, and how to use it. Looking for documentation on how to build a GraphQL service? There are libraries to help you implement GraphQL in many different languages. For an in-depth learning experience with practical tutorials, see How to GraphQL. Check out the free online course, Exploring GraphQL: A Query Language for APIs.</p>

